asset.hookText:
Recording artist Ellie Goulding turns it up on the road and the stage. Take a peek into how running fits into her life as an artist and on the road. Listen to her talk about training for the inaugural Nike Women Half Marathon in Washington, DC. 4.28.13. Let's turn it up.
